inum|number=3|refname=BPI|salesamount=2,000,000+ |salesref=<ref>https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/max-martins-official-top-40-biggest-songs__26246/</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|certyear=2016|relyear=2016|artist=Justin Timberlake|title=Can't Stop the Feeling!|type=single|award=Platinum|number=4|refname=RIAA|salesamount=3,280,000 |salesref=<ref name=\"digital\"/>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==Release history==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Country\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n! scope=\"col\"| Label\n! scope=\"col\"| {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | United States\n| rowspan=\"2\"| May 6, 2016\n| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| [[RCA Records|RCA]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01F49DZEO|title=Can't Stop the Feeling!|publisher=|accessdate=November 9, 2016|work=Amazon}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| [[Sony Music Entertainment|Sony]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://radiodate.it/radio-date/justin-timberlake-can-t-stop-the-feeling-original-song-from-dreamworks-animation-s-trolls-144546-06-05-2016-radiodate/|title=Justin Timberlake \u2013 Can't Stop the Feeling! RadioDate|accessdate=May 15, 2016|date=May 6, 2016|work=Radioairplay.fm}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | United States\n| May 10, 2016\n| RCA\n| <ref name=\"chr\">{{cite web | url=http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases | title=Top 40/M | publisher=All Access Music Group | accessdate=May 6, 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510105348/http://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases |archivedate=May 10, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Germany\n| July 15, 2016\n| [[CD single]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| Sony\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.de/Cant-Stop-Feeling-Original-Dreamw/dp/B01HFRBHYI|title=Can't Stop the Feeling! (Original Song from DreamW|date=July 15, 2016|pu