ibute\">{{cite web|title=American Sociological Association|url=http://www.asanet.org/news-events/footnotes/apr-may-2019/features/tribute-erik-olin-wright-103rd-asa-president|accessdate=May 7, 2019|date=April 18, 2019}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"utopias\">{{Cite book|title = Envisioning Real Utopias|last = Wright|first = Erik Olin|publisher = Verso|year = 2010|isbn = 978-1-84467-618-7|location = London, New York|pages = 321}}</ref>\n}}\n\n== Further reading ==\n* Vivek Chibber, [https://web.archive.org/web/20190125183537/https://www.jacobinmag.com/2019/01/erik-olin-wright-obituary-class-marxism \"Erik Olin Wright (1947\u20132019),\"] ''Jacobin,'' Jan. 24, 2019.\n* Adam Szetela, [https://www.dissentmagazine.org/blog/remembering-erik-olin-wright \"Remembering Erik Olin Wright,\"] ''Dissent'',\" Jan. 23, 2019.\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.ssc.wisc.edu/~wright/ Erik Olin Wright's website]\n* [http://www.oxonianreview.org/wp/a-rough-guide-to-utopia/ 'A Rough Guide to Utopia'], review of ''Envisioning Real Utopias'' in the ''[[Oxonian Review]]'', November 2010\n* [http://www.dissentmagazine.org/article/real-men-find-real-utopias 'Real Men Find Real Utopias'], review of ''Envisioning Real Utopias'' in ''[[Dissent (American magazine)|Dissent (magazine)]]'', Winter 2011\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083532/http://ias.umn.edu/2007/12/01/wright-erik-olin/ 'Conversation with Peter Shea at University of Minnesota, 2007']\n\n{{American Sociological Association presidents}}\n{{September group}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Wright, Erik Olin}}\n[[Category:American sociologists]]\n[[Category:Jewish sociologists]]\n[[Category:Jewish American social scientists]]\n[[Category:American Marxists]]\n[[Category:Marxist theorists]]\n[[Category:New Left]]\n[[Category:University of Wisconsin\u2013Madison faculty]]\n[[Category:Harvard College alumni]]\n[[Category:Alumni of Balliol College, Oxford]]\n[[Category:University of California, Berkeley alumni]]\n[[Category:People